siccom.sim

Class Config

  • java.lang.Object
    • siccom.sim.Config

  • public class Config
extends java.lang.Object
    In this file all the parameters from the parameter files are passed on to the program. GUI input is handled differently in the bottom part.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Andreas Kubicek
